ormal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n依家連玩新電腦既心機都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（好彩銀包同買電腦既cash分開左放 唔你我真心去IFC 跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">薄酬</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/110332_d615451e2c341403176d7d4d3dac14d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F110332_d615451e2c341403176d7d4d3dac14d9.jpg&h=ba2180d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nexactly呢一款<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 我呻完好啲啦 <br />\n利申：借friend ac 開po"},{"pid":"ac0224e5b5040ce92e3721311761da9cc4f3fd9e","tid":374684,"uid":25034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日本來好開心咁去黃金買電腦，幾年冇買新電腦所以好興奮，途中八達通冇錢去港鐵增值 。<br />\n<br />\n點知，屌銀包唔知去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （習慣銀包同八達通分開放），咁平時自己都算係粗心大意既人啦，就以為漏左係屋值冇理到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，問個friend借住錢先，再好開心咁買電腦，再係佢屋企試機試到夜晚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12點幾</span>。<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企，仆街，反轉屋企都冇，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我醒起我同一日朝早有拎過銀包出黎買早餐，心中已知gg。。。。<br />\n<br />\n銀包入面有現金、身份證、回鄉證同<span style=\"color: red;\">好多好多有名既卡</span>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要係我隻usb呀！入面有以前讀中學sports day 、打比賽同球隊影既相。全部回憶一次唔見晒，依家崩潰左<img src=\"/ass